to a variety store off base latrines were down the street so were 
a hastily constructed set of showers 
sunset came with a hint of relief from the days dusty heat as 
three members of the 265th took up guard duty stopping vehicles 
coming onto post the m16s on their shoulders werent loaded 
clips of ammunition were in their pockets 
