the targets lay spreadeagle on a 
mound of dirt sheldon smith leveled his 12gauge shotgun and 
gleefully pumped away aiming mainly for the knees and ankles 
when the smoke cleared another set of blue jeans lay crumpled 
on the chewedup embankment riddled with holes 
