officials said 
at least 14000 people have been killed in the insurrection 
which broke out in 1983 tamils who make up 18 percent of sri 
lankas 16 million people accuse the sinhalese of discrimination 
sinhalese constitute 75 percent of the population of this island 
off the southern tip of india 
