represented another step in his official reemergence in the soviet 
union his longbanned books are being published in the nation that 
expelled him in 1974 for treason and last month president mikhail 
gorbachev ordered his citizenship restored 
komsomolskaya pravdas circulation is 22 million the article 
also will be published in this weeks literaturnaya gazeta a 
literary journal with a circulation of 45 million 
individuals sick with severe illnesses 
such as lung cancer and in great financial need get paid before 
those with less pressing ailments 
weinstein appointed a former federal judge marvin frankel to 
hold hearings on whether a class action is warranted on the claims 
against the manville trust 
after similar hearings frankel earlier this month ruled that 
eaglepicher qualified for a class action the company which makes 
industrial products has more than 64000 lawsuits pending and is 
being named in 20000 more a year 
frankel said eaglepicher faces insolvency because of its 
liability weinstein is expected to rule on whether to approve a 
class action at a hearing next week though lawyers for the company 
and plaintiffs have not yet agreed on how the money would be paid 
in such a settlement 
in addition to a financial restructuring covered by manvilles 
520 million infusion weinstein has ordered the trust to alter the 
way it pays claims to meet those with the greatest need first 
currently claims are resolved based the time of filing 
