york lottery four years ago also ran into probolems said naste 
after receiving a check for around 148000 the first of his 
20 annual aftertax installments he quit his 38000ayear job 
threw a party and put 10000 down on each of 10 new cadillacs he 
said 
but in the next eight months six of the luxury cars were 
repossessed and the man had to borrow 200000 to hold him over 
between lottery checks naste said 
