percent in august pushed up by the energy price spiral set in 
motion by iraqs aug 2 seizure of kuwait 
the gain in the consumer price index which was within the range 
of market expectations was double the 04 percent rise in july and 
the largest since january when a severe cold snap pushed costs up 
11 percent 
