the session following a sharp decline on the london metal exchange 
that analysts attributed to disappointed selling by traders who had 
expected strong gains 
those expectations stemmed from perceptions that a squeeze 
or partial corner of the copper market was developing in london 
where options on september copper deliveries are nearing 
expiration 
