bargaining committee chairs will vote on the tentative pact before 
its sent to the rank and file for formal ratification that 
process is expected to be completed by the end of the month 
if ratified the contract will be used by the union as a model 
for agreements with ford and chrysler union agreements with those 
two companies which cover more than 150000 active workers also 
expired at midnight friday the union put talks with those 
automakers on hold pending the outcome of the gm ratification vote 
