hunter group inc offered last week to buy corroon amp black for 40 
a share in cash or about 840 million 
under the approved agreement corroon amp black stockholders would 
receive 78 willis faber shares for each corroon amp black share or 
3349 at current market prices in a deal valued at 754 million 
