in october issue 
more than half provide child care either in or near the 
workplace 20 percent help with care for aging relatives and a 
growing number are offering paid paternity leaves of at least one 
week 
the latest list was expanded to 75 companies from the 60 a year 
earlier and more than double the 30 companies that appeared in the 
initial ranking published in 1986 
